Show HN: FederAI – Twitter growth and engagement tool for small accounts
text:
Hey all!

I built an AI-assist Twitter growth and engagement tool for small accounts as most other tools focus on growing medium to large account

My goal is to make it easy to come up with quality content daily and make connections with other accounts in less time.

On a daily basis, you will receive 8 Ready-to-use personalized tweets, prompts, and related viral tweets in your inbox. You will be able to search through to 2M+ viral tweets library or let the AI do it thing. Analytics, thread scheduling, and multi-account are supported out of the box so you don't have to install multiple apps.

I would love any feedback from you all.

Hope you all enjoy :)

Check it out here: https://federai.co

Twitter: https://twitter.com/domng_me
